INSTALL:
You need to install:
- scapy version > 2.0, available as a package in ubuntu or at http://www.secdev.org/projects/scapy/
- python-progressbar, availabe as a package in ubuntu or at http://pypi.python.org/pypi/progressbar
- python, of course
- python-pcapy
- python-impacket

HELP
For help, type
python run.py --help

EX.
python run.py -s $SND_CAP_FILE_ETH -r $RCVD_CAP_FILE_PPP --data-sender-mac=$SND_MAC --save-report=report.log

You need to supply --data-*-mac argument for each cap file with an ethernet header

